  "title": "Production & Warehouse Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>To maintain a clean and hygienic environment for production and warehouse workers. <br /><br />This is a 1-year contract position. Upon completion, any extension or renewal will be subject to management's approval.</p><p><strong>A) </strong><u><strong> For Production Area</strong></u></p><ul><li>General cleaning such as sweeping and mopping of floor</li><li>Disposal of rubbish</li></ul><p><strong>B) </strong><u><strong> For Warehouse Area</strong></u></p><ul><li>General cleaning such as sweeping of floor</li><li>Disposal of rubbish</li></ul><p><u><strong>C)  Ad-hoc Cleaning Duties</strong></u></p><ul><li>Help out with office carpet cleaning once every six months</li><li>Ad-hoc cleaning duties may be assigned when necessary</li></ul><p></p><p>Working Location: Kallang, Genting Lane area</p><p>Working Days: Monday - Friday</p><p>Working Time: 8.30am - 5.30pm</p>",
